  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n1. Add a reaction to 1-1 or any chat or community message\r\n2. Check the frame of the reaction\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nThe frame of a reaction has a constant thickness\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n<img width=\"435\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/14942081/171760004-2b8b4fe9-dcf2-4a34-b149-ca5a9620c96c.png\">\r\n\r\n![unknown (7)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/176720/181103051-e90b0fbd-ac94-44d6-b190-f53474fd5920.png)\r\n\r\n\r\nThe frame of a reaction doesn't have a constant thickness\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\nStatus desktop version: https://ci.status.im/job/status-desktop/job/branches/job/macos/job/master/2151/\r\nOperating System: macOS Monterey 12.3 Beta (21E5227a)\r\n\r\n",
